# 🍕 Pizza Sales Dashboard – Excel Project

## 📌 Overview
This project analyzes pizza sales data using Microsoft Excel to uncover insights on sales trends, popular products, and revenue. The goal is to help a fictional pizza business make better data-driven decisions.

## 📁 Dataset
- 48,621 rows and 12 columns
- Includes order date, time, pizza size, ingredients, revenue, etc.

## ⚙ Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel
- Power Query
- Pivot Tables
- Excel Functions
- Excel Charts

## 📊 Key KPIs
- Total Revenue: $817,860
- Total Orders: 48,620
- Most Ordered Pizza: Classic Deluxe
- Highest Revenue Pizza: Thai Chicken
- Average Order Value: $16.82

## 📈 Key Insights
- Afternoon and Friday are peak sales times
- Large size and Classic category are most popular
- XX-Large has lowest sales — recommendation to discontinue

## 📄 Files Included
- `Pizza_Sales_Dashboard.xlsx`: The final Excel file with dashboard
- `Pizza_Sales_Cleaned.xlsx`: Cleaned dataset
- `README.md`: Project description (this file)

## 💡 What I Learned
- Data cleaning with Power Query
- Using formulas to extract time-based insights
- Dashboard storytelling using Excel visuals

